  "title": "🎤 Consumer Sales & Events Associate (Entry-Level)",
  "description": "<p>Looking for a role that gets you <strong>out of the office</strong>, meeting people and building real-world skills?<br />Join our team and be part of exciting consumer campaigns, events, and roadshows across Singapore.</p><h3>What You’ll Do</h3><ul><li><p>Represent well-known brands at events, roadshows, and pop-up campaigns</p></li><li><p>Engage consumers through face-to-face interactions</p></li><li><p>Understand customer needs and promote relevant solutions</p></li><li><p>Work closely with a supportive team to achieve campaign targets</p></li></ul><h3>What We’re Looking For</h3><ul><li><p>Strong communication skills and a positive attitude</p></li><li><p>Comfortable interacting with people</p></li><li><p>Willingness to learn — <strong>no prior experience required</strong></p></li><li><p>Team players who enjoy a fast-paced environment</p></li></ul><h3>What You’ll Gain</h3><ul><li><p>Hands-on experience in sales, events & consumer marketing</p></li><li><p>Coaching and on-the-job training provided</p></li><li><p>Performance-based incentives and growth opportunities</p></li><li><p>Fun, energetic, and supportive team culture</p></li></ul><p>📍 Location: Singapore<br />⏱️ Start: Immediate / Flexible<br />🎓 Open to fresh grads, career switchers, and entry-level candidates</p><p>👉 <strong>Apply now</strong> to find out if this role is a good fit for you.</p>",
